---
title: Capture and canonicalize a job observation
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Client as HTMX UI / Extension / CSV import
    participant Boundary as Django / DRF capture boundary
    participant Idem as Idempotency mechanism
    participant Bridge as Integrations / Data Bridge
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Outbox as Outbox dispatcher
    participant Broker as RabbitMQ
    participant Worker as Celery worker
    participant Registry as Job Registry service

    User->>Client: Submit capture or import
    Client->>Boundary: Capture request
    Boundary->>Idem: Check key and request fingerprint

    alt Unexpired retry with identical request
        Idem-->>Boundary: Existing acceptance response
        Boundary-->>Client: 202 + existing operation location
    else New request
        rect rgb(239, 246, 255)
            Note over Bridge,DB: Atomic transport-acceptance transaction
            Boundary->>Bridge: Accept payload and provenance
            Bridge->>DB: Check envelope replay
            alt Envelope replay
                DB-->>Bridge: Existing envelope
            else New envelope
                Bridge->>DB: Persist immutable InboundEnvelope
                Bridge->>DB: Persist operation, audit, and outbox events
                DB-->>Bridge: Commit
            end
        end

        Bridge-->>Boundary: Accepted envelope and operation
        Boundary->>Idem: Store 202 acceptance response
        Boundary-->>Client: 202 Accepted + Location
    end

    Outbox->>DB: Poll unpublished envelope events
    DB-->>Outbox: envelope.accepted
    Outbox->>Broker: Publish event
    Broker->>Worker: Deliver contract-processing task

    Worker->>DB: Read immutable envelope
    Worker->>Worker: Validate and translate provider-neutral contract
    Worker->>Registry: Accept job evidence
    Registry->>DB: Check exact source replay

    alt Exact source replay
        DB-->>Registry: Existing JobObservation
    else New observation or source revision
        Registry->>DB: Persist immutable JobObservation and outbox event
        Registry->>DB: Commit
    end

    Worker->>DB: Persist versioned normalization
    Worker->>Worker: Resolve job identity
    Worker->>DB: Commit resolution transaction
    Worker->>DB: Complete operation result

    Client->>Boundary: GET operation status
    Boundary->>DB: Read current operation
    DB-->>Boundary: completed / ambiguous / failed
    Boundary-->>Client: HTML fragment or API representation
